ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.points

Class POIPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.points.Point
      • ch.epfl.sdp.peakar.points.POIPoint

  • public class POIPoint
extends Point
    POIPoint is a class that extends Point.java and represents a POI in the map. It provides a constructor to build a POIPoint from a org.osmdroid.util.GeoPoint.
